author: Darrell Moody
title: Alumni notebook: How Carson City area athletes are doing on college
text: Related Media FOOTBALL Colby Brown (Carson-College of Idaho): Scored first collegiate TD on a 16-yard TD run last weekend. Had 6 carries for 23 yards. Dylan Sawyers (Carson-Feather River): No game last week. Nevin Elliott (Carson-College of San Mateo): No game last week. Logan Krupp (Carson-Western Oregon): No stats in a 24-22 win over No. Alabama. Did have 2 tackles the week prior in win over Dixie State. Josh Joyner (Dayton-Western Oregon): No stats in 24-22 win over No. Alabama. Did have a tackle week prior against Dixie State. Andrew Gutierrez (Carson-Feather River): No game last week. Julio Meza (Dayton-George Fox): Didn’t see action last week against Lewis & Clark. Joey Thurman (Carson-Yuba College): No game last week. Jonathan Joyner (Dayton-George Fox): Didn’t see action last week against Lewis & Clark. Skyler Berntson (Dayton-Southwest Baptist): Played but recorded no stats in 23-14 loss to Truman. SOCCER Michelle Sandage (Carson-William Jessup): Team went 0-2 last week. Started both games, no goals or assists. Kenzie Tillitt (Carson, Colorado): Played in one match last week, no stats. Bailie Zuber (Carson-Peninsula College): Played in two wins last week, no goals or assists. Brenda Torres (Carson-Peninsula College): Had one goal in two wins last week. Josilyn Daggs (Carson-University of Idaho): Had an assist on a throw-in in 3-1 win over Montana. CROSS COUNTRY Becky Grabow (Sierra Lutheran-UOP): No meet last week. Nathaneal Williams (Sierra Lutheran-Colorado Mines): No meet last week. VOLLEYBALL Cheyanne Strong (Dayton-Umpqua College): Had 7 kills and 1 dig in loss to Linn-Benton. Madison Foley (Dayton-Nevada): Pack lost to UNLV and Fresno State. Had 26 kills and 14 digs for the week. Taryn Schriner (Dayton-W. New Mexico University): Had 1 kill in wins over Adams State and Fort Lewis. Danielle Good (Carson-Cabrillo College): No matches last week. Did we miss someone? Send an email to sports@nevadaappeal.com.
